INSERT INTO `chatbot_logs` VALUES (1,1,'What clubs are available at SEGI University?','We have 3 clubs available:\n\n1. SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC) - Hobby\n2. Youth of Hope (SEGI Islamic Club) - Cultural\n3. SRC SEGI University - Academic\n\nLet me know if you\'d like to know more about any of these clubs!','2026-06-05 13:02:36','session1'),(2,2,'how to join vision club','To join SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC), you can fill out their membership form here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform?pli=1 \n\nYou can also reach out to them on Instagram: @segivmac for more info.','2026-06-11 11:59:27','session1'),(3,2,'Show me all clubs','Here are the current clubs:\n\n1. **SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC)** - Hobby\n   Description: A creative community where talents and creativity are welcomed.\n   Contact: @segivmac (Instagram)\n   Membership: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform\n\n2. **SRC SEGI University** - Academic\n   Description: Student Representative Council.\n   Contact: @srcsegiuni (Instagram)\n   Membership: N/A\n\n3. **Youth of Hope (Segi Islamic Club)** - Cultural\n   Description: A journey of knowledge, compassion, and spiritual growth.\n   Contact: @segi.youthofhope\n   Membership: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdyVhAZzn4xeaUsUl_rtM_vyPVL9twQw5jMNQ9EMh61zyKN-w/viewform\n\nLet me know if you need more info!','2026-06-26 11:34:59',NULL),(4,2,'How do I register for a club?','To register for a club, you can check the club\'s membership link. Some clubs have a Google form link, like SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC) and Youth of Hope (Segi Islamic Club). Just click on the link and fill out the form. If a club doesn\'t have a link, you can try contacting them through their Instagram account.','2026-06-27 20:15:55',NULL),(5,2,'Recommend a club for me','I\'d like to recommend the SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC). It\'s a hobby club that welcomes creativity and talents. They seem to have fun events, like the upcoming \"Splash & Spill\" party. You can check them out on Instagram @segivmac and even join through their membership form if you\'re interested!','2026-06-28 01:57:14',NULL),(6,3,'What sports clubs are available?','We have several sports clubs available, including:\n\n1. Segi Basketball Club\n2. Segi Volleyball Club\n3. Segi Taekwondo\n4. Segi University Badminton Club\n\nLet me know if you\'d like more information about any of these clubs!','2026-06-28 02:03:32',NULL),(7,2,'how to join volley ball club?','To join the Segi Volleyball Club, you can fill out their membership form here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrpZFOR150mdFGK8YtLy8NVNCHryTdxsy5bUbs5eLLW9VWHw/formResponse \n\nYou can also contact them at @segivolleyball for more information.','2026-06-29 16:21:52',NULL),(8,3,'how to join basketball club','To join the Segi Basketball Club, you can sign up through their Instagram page: https://www.instagram.com/segibasketballclubkd. You can also contact them directly at @segibasketballclubkd for more information.','2026-06-29 17:20:24',NULL),(9,2,'any upcoming event?','Yes, there are several upcoming events. Here are a few:\n\n1. ROYAL STARLIGHT - PROM NIGHT 2026 (July 3)\n2. 2026 SEGI 3X3 (July 2)\n3. TALENT SHOW (July 10)\n4. GLITCH & GLAM (July 16)\n\nYou can find more details about these events, including the venue and time. Would you like to know more about a specific event?','2026-06-29 18:18:48',NULL),(10,3,'hpw to jin volunteer','You can join the Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC) by filling out their membership form: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform \n\nYou can also contact them at @suvc.official for more info!','2026-06-29 20:25:42',NULL),(11,3,'What events are happening this week?','I don\'t have the current date, but I can show you events happening around the dates I have. \n\nThere\'s \"TALENT SHOW\" by Segi International Student Society(siss) on Fri Jul 10, and \"GLITCH & GLAM\" by Student Representative Council on Thu Jul 16. \n\nIf you\'d like more info or specific dates, feel free to ask!','2026-06-30 11:14:47',NULL),(12,3,'Which tech club should I join?','We don\'t have a specific tech club available. However, you might be interested in joining the SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC) as they focus on multimedia and arts, which may involve some tech aspects. You can join them through this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform?pli=1','2026-06-30 11:15:06',NULL),(13,3,'Show me all clubs','Here are the clubs at SEGI University:\n\n1. **SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC)** - Hobby (@segivmac)\n2. **Student Representative Council** - Academic (@srcsegiuni)\n3. **Youth of Hope (Segi Islamic Club)** - Cultural (@segi.youthofhope)\n4. **Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC)** - Community (@suvc.official)\n5. **Segi Basketball Club** - Sports (@segibasketballclubkd)\n6. **Segi Volleyball Club** - Sports (@segivolleyball)\n7. **Segi International Student Society(siss)** - Cultural (sisssegi)\n8. **Segi Taekwondo Club** - Sports (@segitaekwondo)\n9. **Segi Mozambique Community** - Cultural (segimz)\n10. **Global Djiboutian Network** - Community (globaldjiboutian)\n11. **Segi Pakistan** - Community (segipakistan)\n12. **Segi Maldivan Society** - Cultural (segimv.society)\n13. **Malay Cultural Society Segi** - Cultural (@mcssegi_)\n14. **Segi Optometry Club (SOC)** - Academic (@segioptometry)\n15. **Segi Psychology Club** - Academic (@segipsychologyclub)\n\nLet me know if you need more info!','2026-07-05 21:22:29',NULL),(14,3,'how to knit?','I can help you find a club related to knitting, but I don\'t have a specific guide on how to knit. However, I can suggest joining the SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC) as they are a hobby club and might have resources or members who can help you with knitting. You can join them through this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform?pli=1','2026-07-05 21:54:05',NULL),(15,3,'Recommend a club for me','What are your interests? Do you like sports, music, community work, or something else? This will help me suggest a club that\'s a good fit for you.','2026-07-07 00:50:24',NULL),(16,3,'sports','We have several sports clubs at SEGI University. Here are a few:\n\n1. Segi Basketball Club - @segibasketballclubkd\n2. Segi Volleyball Club - @segivolleyball\n3. Segi Taekwondo Club - @segitaekwondo\n\nWhich one are you interested in? I can provide you with the join link.','2026-07-07 00:50:36',NULL),(17,3,'basketball','You\'re interested in basketball. We have the Segi Basketball Club. You can join them through their Instagram: @segibasketballclubkd. Would you like to know more about the club or get the join link?','2026-07-07 00:50:47',NULL),(18,3,'send the join link','You can join the clubs through these links:\n\n1. SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC) - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform?pli=1\n2. Student Representative Council - https://beacons.ai/srcsegiuni?fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQPOTM2NjE5NzQzMzkyNDU5AAGnwvp58lY5ve5QlukcjFt2OL6ozZQr41FHZRD8_lqYnb0N1h6OiUu2idkhTQk_aem_VO3s0YjNjI2f1zaCZL3Ueg\n3. Youth of Hope (Segi Islamic Club) - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdyVhAZzn4xeaUsUl_rtM_vyPVL9twQw5jMNQ9EMh61zyKN-w/viewform\n4. Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC) - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform\n5. Segi Basketball Club - https://www.instagram.com/segibasketballclubkd?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==\n6. Segi Volleyball Club - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrpZFOR150mdFGK8YtLy8NVNCHryTdxsy5bUbs5eLLW9VWHw/formResponse\n7. Segi International Student Society(siss) - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSccR_LFdGzb2VfVX7KEq3ErqjjhPrdPnCacargOVxB8OfylcQ/closedform\n8. Segi Taekwondo Club - https://linktr.ee/segitaekwondo?utm_source=ig&utm_medium=social&utm_content=link_in_bio&fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQPOTM2NjE5NzQzMzkyNDU5AAGnidhvCn8uLRR_D-3mUvh4QXkz5i5kYcCIELGqZJ5xD7LIsgP7E7kNGfuAkLc_aem_yAvwwAdkYmYtc2aKzn4ZpQ\n9. Segi Mozambique Community - https://www.instagram.com/segi.mz?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==\n10. Global Djiboutian Network - https://www.instagram.com/globaldjiboutian?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==\n11. Segi Pakistan - https://chat.whatsapp.com/BqiTZDl34KsKnVMEwFGNYx\n12. Segi Maldivan Society - https://www.instagram.com/segi.mv.society?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==\n13. Malay Cultural Society Segi - https://linktr.ee/mcssegi?utm_source=ig&utm_medium=social&utm_content=link_in_bio&fbclid=PAZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAc3J0YwZhcHBfaWQPOTM2NjE5NzQzMzkyNDU5AAGnDYJc29zv4svSybsydihCZwFyBu1bCn7WBsWy4aCcNz6aij2Bgzzp6A2a2lA_aem_uyl13n4YmBVdpv-P3smOfA\n14. Segi Optometry Club (SOC) - https://www.instagram.com/segioptometry?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==\n15. Segi Psychology Club - https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSclsnxr1arCTGwPH6eeM_C5gseU8HDmpIcjgroOldwL1V_E5A/viewform\n\nWhich one would you like to join?','2026-07-07 00:51:02',NULL),(19,3,'send join link for basketball only','Here\'s the join link for Segi Basketball Club: https://www.instagram.com/segibasketballclubkd?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw==','2026-07-07 00:51:30',NULL),(20,2,'Recommend a club for me','Let\'s find a club that suits you. What are your interests? (Hobby, Academic, Sports, Cultural, or Community?)','2026-07-07 09:37:56',NULL),(21,2,'What events are happening this week?','Here are the events happening this week:\n\n1. TROPICAL SPARK - Today (Tue Jul 07) at 10:00 AM at Segi University Cafe\n2. E-WASTE AWARENESS DAY - Thu Jul 16 at 11:00 AM at MPH Lobby\n3. GLITCH & GLAM - Thu Jul 16 at 10:00 AM at MPH Segi University \n\nLet me know if you need more info!','2026-07-07 09:38:25',NULL),(22,3,'What events are happening this week?','Here are the events happening this week:\n\n1. TROPICAL SPARK - Today (Tue Jul 07) at 10:00 AM, Segi University Cafe\n2. E-WASTE AWARENESS DAY - Thu Jul 16 at 11:00 AM, MPH Lobby\n3. GLITCH & GLAM - Thu Jul 16 at 10:00 AM, MPH Segi University\n\nLet me know if you\'d like more info!','2026-07-07 12:02:46',NULL),(23,3,'HOW TO JOIN BASKETBALL CLUB','To join the Segi Basketball Club, you can follow this link: https://www.instagram.com/segibasketballclubkd/?utm_source=ig_web_button_share_sheet&igsh=ZDNlZDc0MzIxNw== \n\nJust click on the link, go to their Instagram page, and send them a message to express your interest in joining the club.','2026-07-07 12:03:00',NULL),(24,3,'What events are happening this week?','Here are the events happening this week:\n\n1. TROPICAL SPARK - Today, 10:00 AM at Segi University Cafe\n2. LAKE CLEANUP - Sun, 8:00 AM at Tasik Cova Lake\n3. EVENT GATHERING - Sun, 4:00 PM at SCCL (Near Pool)\n\nLet me know if you need more info!','2026-07-09 16:00:33',NULL),(25,3,'Which tech club should I join?','We don\'t have a specific tech club listed. However, if you\'re interested in tech, you might want to consider joining the Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC) or the Student Representative Council, as they may have events or initiatives related to technology. Alternatively, you could reach out to the SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC) to see if they have any tech-related activities or projects.','2026-07-09 16:00:41',NULL),(26,3,'What events are happening this week?','Here are the events happening this week:\n\n1. TROPICAL SPARK (Today) - 10:00 AM at Segi University Cafe\n2. **LAKE CLEANUP (Sun)**: 8:00 AM at Tasik Cova Lake\n3. **EVENT GATHERING (Sun)**: 4:00 PM at SCCL (Near Pool)\n\nLet me know if you need more info!','2026-07-09 16:00:53',NULL),(27,3,'How do I register for a club?','To register for a club, simply click on the \"Join link\" provided for the specific club you\'re interested in. Each club has its own unique link. You can find the links in the list of clubs I have.','2026-07-09 16:00:59',NULL),(28,3,'What events are coming up?','We have several events coming up. Here are a few:\n\n1. **TROPICAL SPARK** - July 7, 10:00 AM at Segi University Cafe\n2. **EVENT GATHERING** - July 5, 4:00 PM at SCCL (Near Pool)\n3. **LAKE CLEANUP** - July 5, 8:00 AM at Tasik Cova Lake\n4. **MISSION PAWSIBLE** - July 12, 8:00 AM at Zoo Negara Malaysia\n5. **E-WASTE AWARENESS DAY** - July 16, 11:00 AM at MPH Lobby\n6. **GLITCH & GLAM** - July 16, 10:00 AM at MPH Segi University\n7. **CLEAN TRAILS, GREEN FUTURE** - July 18, 1:00 AM at Segi University\n8. **THE GENTLE PROJECT** - July 22, 9:00 AM at SEGi University Library\n\nYou can check out more details and upcoming events on our platform!','2026-07-12 01:44:45','session_1783791882166'),(29,3,'Tell me about volunteering clubs','We have the Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC) which is a community-focused club. You can join them through this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform. They also have an Instagram page @suvc.official. Would you like to know more about their activities?','2026-07-12 01:44:52','session_1783791882166'),(30,2,'What events are coming up?','We have several events coming up. Here are a few:\n\n1. **LAKE CLEANUP** - This Sun, Jul 5, 8:00 AM at Tasik Cova Lake\n2. **EVENT GATHERING** - This Sun, Jul 5, 4:00 PM at SCCL (Near Pool)\n3. **TROPICAL SPARK** - Tue, Jul 7, 10:00 AM at Segi University Cafe\n4. **TALENT SHOW** - Fri, Jul 10, 6:00 PM at Auditorium A\n5. **MISSION PAWSIBLE** - Sun, Jul 12, 8:00 AM at Zoo Negara Malaysia\n6. **E-WASTE AWARENESS DAY** - Thu, Jul 16, 11:00 AM at MPH Lobby\n7. **GLITCH & GLAM** - Thu, Jul 16, 10:00 AM at MPH Segi University\n8. **CLEAN TRAILS, GREEN FUTURE** - Sat, Jul 18, 1:00 AM at Meet at Segi University\n9. **THE GENTLE PROJECT** - Wed, Jul 22, 9:00 AM at SEGi University Library\n\nCheck them out and join the ones that interest you!','2026-07-12 02:43:36','session_1783795410678'),(31,2,'how to join volunteer club','To join the Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC), you can click on this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform\n\nYou can also check out their Instagram: @suvc.official for more info!','2026-07-12 02:43:48','session_1783795410678'),(32,3,'What events are coming up?','We have several events coming up. Here are a few: \n\n1. ROYAL STARLIGHT - PROM NIGHT 2026 on Jul 3\n2. LAKE CLEANUP on Jul 5\n3. EVENT GATHERING on Jul 5\n4. TROPICAL SPARK on Jul 7\n5. TALENT SHOW on Jul 10\n6. MISSION PAWSIBLE on Jul 12\n7. E-WASTE AWARENESS DAY on Jul 16\n8. GLITCH & GLAM on Jul 16\n9. CLEAN TRAILS, GREEN FUTURE on Jul 18\n10. THE GENTLE PROJECT on Jul 22\n\nYou can ask me for more details about a specific event if you\'re interested!','2026-07-12 11:48:57','session_1783828132276'),(33,2,'Show me all clubs','Here are the clubs at SEGI University:\n\n1. **SEGI Vision Multimedia & Arts Club (SEGI VMAC)** - Hobby - @segivmac - [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScEJTxczKOFzGdEabguPgWQU20LwIyUcFjyfvp-tq_i8acJoQ/viewform)\n2. **Student Representative Council** - Academic - @srcsegiuni - [https://beacons.ai/srcsegiuni](https://beacons.ai/srcsegiuni)\n3. **Youth of Hope (Segi Islamic Club)** - Cultural - @segi.youthofhope - [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdyVhAZzn4xeaUsUl_rtM_vyPVL9twQw5jMNQ9EMh61zyKN-w/viewform](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdyVhAZzn4xeaUsUl_rtM_vyPVL9twQw5jMNQ9EMh61zyKN-w/viewform)\n4. **Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC)** - Community - @suvc.official - [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform)\n5. **Segi Basketball Club** - Sports - @segibasketballclubkd - [https://www.instagram.com/segibasketballclubkd](https://www.instagram.com/segibasketballclubkd)\n6. **Segi Volleyball Club** - Sports - @segivolleyball - [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrpZFOR150mdFGK8YtLy8NVNCHryTdxsy5bUbs5eLLW9VWHw/formResponse](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrpZFOR150mdFGK8YtLy8NVNCHryTdxsy5bUbs5eLLW9VWHw/formResponse)\n7. **Segi International Student Society(siss)** - Cultural - @sisssegi - [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSccR_LFdGzb2VfVX7KEq3ErqjjhPrdPnCacargOVxB8OfylcQ/closedform](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSccR_LFdGzb2VfVX7KEq3ErqjjhPrdPnCacargOVxB8OfylcQ/closedform)\n8. **Segi Taekwondo Club** - Sports - @segitaekwondo - [https://linktr.ee/segitaekwondo](https://linktr.ee/segitaekwondo)\n9. **Segi Mozambique Community** - Cultural - @segimz - [https://www.instagram.com/segi.mz](https://www.instagram.com/segi.mz)\n10. **Global Djiboutian Network** - Community - @globaldjiboutian - [https://www.instagram.com/globaldjiboutian](https://www.instagram.com/globaldjiboutian)\n11. **Segi Pakistan** - Community - @segipakistan - [https://chat.whatsapp.com/BqiTZDl34KsKnVMEwFGNYx](https://chat.whatsapp.com/BqiTZDl34KsKnVMEwFGNYx)\n12. **Segi Maldivan Society** - Cultural - @segimv.society - [https://www.instagram.com/segi.mv.society](https://www.instagram.com/segi.mv.society)\n13. **Malay Cultural Society Segi** - Cultural - @mcssegi_ - [https://linktr.ee/mcssegi](https://linktr.ee/mcssegi)\n14. **Segi Optometry Club (SOC)** - Academic - @segioptometry - [https://www.instagram.com/segioptometry](https://www.instagram.com/segioptometry)\n15. **Segi Psychology Club** - Academic - @segipsychologyclub - [https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSclsnxr1arCTGwPH6eeM_C5gseU8HDmpIcjgroOldwL1V_E5A/viewform](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSclsnxr1arCTGwPH6eeM_C5gseU8HDmpIcjgroOldwL1V_E5A/viewform)\n\nLet me know if you need more info!','2026-07-12 11:50:32','session_1783828229028'),(34,2,'Tell me about volunteering clubs','We have the Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC) which focuses on community service. You can join them through this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform. They also have an Instagram account @suvc.official if you\'d like to learn more about their activities!','2026-07-12 11:52:31','session_1783828347615'),(35,2,'the link isnt working','Sorry to hear that the link isn\'t working. Can you please tell me which club or event\'s link is not working? I\'ll try to help you find an alternative way to join or get more information.','2026-07-12 11:53:34','session_1783828395121'),(36,2,'volunteer club','The Segi University Volunteer Club (SUVC) is a community club. \n\nInstagram: @suvc.official\nJoin link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfbN6rxq7GXz17IhMct_VLRKejPNAmmztRT8s_GBbl18mSi-w/viewform\n\nWould you like to join or know more about their activities?','2026-07-12 11:53:52','session_1783828395121'),(37,2,'How do I get notifications from clubs?','To get notifications from clubs, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. **Join the club**: Click on the join link provided for the club you\'re interested in.\n2. **Follow their Instagram**: Follow the club\'s Instagram account to stay updated on their events and activities.\n3. **Check the Community Hub regularly**: Keep an eye on the Community Hub for updates on upcoming events and activities from various clubs.\n\nBy doing so, you\'ll be able to stay informed about the clubs\' activities and events!','2026-07-12 11:55:23','session_1783828520043'),(38,3,'how to join volleyball','To join the Segi Volleyball Club, you can sign up through this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrpZFOR150mdFGK8YtLy8NVNCHryTdxsy5bUbs5eLLW9VWHw/formResponse \n\nYou can also follow them on Instagram @segivolleyball for more information.','2026-07-12 20:44:31','session_1783860215900');
