come the Year of the Horse together!','2026-02-27 12:30:00','R2.5',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783926094/k6lgjajpx3mutzy4cdvr.png'),(68,34,'PRAISE & WORSHIP','? Praise & Worship\nMark your calendars! Join us for an uplifting session of praise and worship.\n\n?️ 6 March | 12:30 PM - 2:30 PM\n? Venue: VCR\n✨ Bring your heart, bring your voice—let’s worship together.','2026-03-06 12:30:00','VCR',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783926196/newdwjtotgatpxvdujbn.png'),(69,34,'PASSION FOR CHRIST','? Get ready to be inspired! ?\nOur Passion for Christ event is happening this Friday, March 13th! ? Join the Youth Ablaze community for an incredible afternoon of worship, connection, and pure joy. You won’t want to miss this! ✨\n\n? When: 12:30 PM – 2:30 PM\n? Where: VCR\n\nBring your friends, bring your energy, and let’s make it a day to remember! See you there! ?️?','2026-03-13 12:30:00','VCR',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783926284/dreebs8pdnd7imzf1qci.png'),(70,34,'CAPTAIN BALL','? Captain Ball Tournament\n\nReady, set, play! Join us for an exciting evening of Captain Ball.\n\n?️ 19 March | 5:00 PM - 7:00 PM\n? Venue: MPH\n? Team up, have fun, and let’s get active! All skill levels welcome.','2026-03-19 17:00:00','MPH',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783926379/alsktx7egp2cpbxxpp8r.png'),(71,34,'JOURNEY TO THE CROSS','“Journey to the Cross” Good Friday - 2026\n\nThis Easter, Youth Ablaze Christian Fellowship invites you to step back in time and explore the story of the first Easter more than 2000 years ago.\n\nCome journey with us through the final days and hours of the life of Jesus - explored through interactive stations designed to engage your senses: what you see, hear, and even taste.\n\nIt’s not just an exhibition but it’s an experience.\n\nWhether you’re curious, searching, or just coming with friends, we hope you’ll walk away discovering what Easter is really all about, and