se for your life on campus and beyond!\n','2026-06-26 12:30:00','R4.2',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783926923/o92dwua2rbckgwxsf1ks.png'),(76,34,'PRAISE & WORSHIP','\"Let everything that has breath praise the Lord!\"\n~ Psalm 150:6\n\nJoin us for a time of Praise & Worship; and testimony sharing by our friends from the mission team all the way from South Perth Uniting Church (SPUC) ?\n\n? Praise & Worship\n? Friday, 3rd July 2026\n? 12:30 PM – 2:30 PM\n? Venue: SCCL 2\n','2026-07-03 12:30:00','SCCL 2',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783927021/y74tpccuapoia3ywv8d0.png'),(77,34,'BOARD GAMES','Roll the dice, steal the win, and make new friends!!! ??\nBoard Games are back!\nWho\'s bringing the snacks? ?\n\n? Thursday, 9 July 2026\n⏰ 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM\n? R2.5\n\nWe will then head over to MCD Petronas Kota Damansara DT for dinner. Food is self-funded.\n\nSee you there!','2026-07-09 17:00:00','R2.5',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783927126/thyerlohyxoqsm9zarrg.png'),(78,3,'MRT TOUR JOURNEY','?✨ MRT Tour Registration is OPEN! ✨?\nHeyy all SEGians!!! Get ready for an exciting city adventure as we explore the MRT together??\n\n? Itinerary & schedule are subject to change, but the fun is guaranteed!\nSpots are limited, so register now and don’t miss out! ?️?\n\n✅ Registration is FREE!\nParticipants will only need to pay for:\n• Touch ‘n Go (TnG) card (if you don’t already have one)\n• Your own lunch expenses ?️\n\nRegister using the link below:\n? https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfVfC_mUMYPo1o0v0GiyVb4xSZ3ucrNUW21ZsjQjjytBXILVg/viewform?usp=publish-editor\nOr scan the QR code!! ?✨','2026-02-07 13:00:00','Meet at MRT',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783929490/db0ldkbpmxx5fquxcl9q.png'),(79,37,'BRIEFING ON PRE-SCHOOL CURRICULUM 2026 WORKSHOP','Preschool Curriculum 2026 Workshop is set to inspire, inform, and empower future educators with fresh perspectives on curriculum change and national priorities. ??‍??‍?\n\n? 4th March 2026\n⏰ 10:00am – 5:00pm\n? Auditorium A, SEGi University\n? Compulsory for all B.Ed students\n\nAn event full of learning, networking, and shaping tomorrow’s classrooms. ?','2026-03-04 10:00:00','Auditorium A',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783933457/hf7gwdd06vihji11m7yy.png'),(80,30,'LOVE, LIES & LONELINESS','? 22nd April 2026\n⏰ 3:00 PM – 4:00 PM\n? Microsoft Teams: Scan Qr Code\nMeeting ID: 438 503 191 445 37\nPasscode: C82wh77w\n\n? This ONLINE TALK has been registered under SEP for KD SEGian Students:\nSEGian Students: https://segikd.segi.edu.my/sep/student/login.html ( First-time SEP registration: account activation takes 2–5 working days) . If you encounter any issues with SEP, please email SEP@segi.edu.my\n\nSave your spot now—this conversation might change the way you see online relationships forever.','2026-04-22 15:00:00','Microsoft Teams ',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783933933/n7p7315ldjjocxalwlen.png'),(81,30,'HOOKED ON THE GAME: THE IMPACT OF GAMING ADDICTION','Join us to explore:\n✨ Signs of gaming addiction\n✨ How it impacts your mental health & academic performance\n✨ Simple ways to regain control (without quitting gaming!)\n? 20 May 2026 (Wed) | ⏰ 3:00 PM – 4:00 PM\n? Open to the public & SEGi students\nCome and learn how to stay in control—without giving up what you enjoy.\n\n? Microsoft Teams\nLink: : https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/48888891774270?p=JtKRjmFPO1XUPuIc6Y\nMeeting ID: 488 888 917 742 70\nPasscode: KU2E5Mw7\n\n? This ONLINE TALK has been registered under SEP for KD SEGian Students:\nSEGian Students: https://segikd.segi.edu.my/sep/student/login.html ( First-time SEP registration: account activation takes 2–5 working days) . If you encounter any issues with SEP, please email SEP@segi.edu.my','2026-05-20 15:00:00','Microsoft Teams',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783934076/rbsazs5hjwxxacq5uhio.png'),(82,30,'CLICKS & CONSEQUENCES','⚠️ “Congratulations! You’ve won a prize.”\n? “I need help urgently.”\n? “Guaranteed high returns with zero risk.”\nScams don’t always look dangerous — sometimes, they look convincing, emotional, and trustworthy. One click is all it takes.\n\nJoin us in this eye-opening webinar as we explore:\n? Why people fall for scams\n? The psychological tactics scammers use\n⚠️ Common online scam trends in Malaysia\n?️ Practical ways to protect yourself and others online\n\n? Webinar: Clicks & Consequences — The Psychology Behind Online Scams\n?‍? Open to SEGi Students and Public\n? 10 June 2026 (Wednesday)\n⏰ 3.00 PM – 4.00 PM\n? Microsoft Teams https://teams.microsoft.com/meet/4123485538318?p=UWnvkJSWRDPZ0eNXiU\nMeeting ID: 412 348 553 831 8\nPasscode: gN9aZ3um\n\nThis ONLINE TALK has been registered under SEP for KD SEGian Students: https://segikd.segi.edu.my/sep/student/login.html ( First-time SEP registration: account activation takes 2–5 working days) . If you encounter any issues with SEP, please email SEP@segi.edu.my','2026-06-10 15:00:00','Microsoft Team',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783934295/dwwvfus6powdmeuaffku.png'),(83,30,'BEYOND THE SILENCE: OVERCOMING LONELINESS WITH POSITIVE PSYCHOLOGY','? Sometimes the hardest part is breaking the silence.\n\nIf you\'ve ever felt lonely, disconnected, or like no one understands what you\'re going through, know that you\'re not alone.\n\nJoin our Group Chat: Beyond the Silence – Overcoming Loneliness with Positive Psychology and discover practical ways to build meaningful connections, strengthen your emotional well-being, and gain a more positive outlook on life.\n\n✨ What you\'ll gain:\n? Better understanding of loneliness and its impact\n? Build meaningful connections\n? Develop healthier ways to cope with loneliness\n?‍⚕️ NOTE: Group Chat has been registered under SEP.\n? Certificate awarded upon completion of all 3 sessions\n\n? Dates: 15, 22 & 29 July 2026 (Wednesday)\n? Time: 3.00 PM – 5.00 PM\n? Venue: Student Activity Room\n\n? Scan the QR code on the poster or click the link below:\nhttps://forms.gle/J8VJko3bDR9S2ngPA (NOTE: FOR SEGIAN STUDENT KOTA DAMANSARA ONLY)','2026-07-15 15:00:00','Student Activity Room',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783934503/xpeqwbdrvvfnqaqysoe5.png'),(84,30,'FINDING EMOTIONAL BALANCE','? Your emotional well-being matters.\n\nFeeling overwhelmed with assignments, stress, or emotions?\n\nYou\'re not alone. ?\nJoin our Group Chat: Finding Emotional Balance with Gestalt Therapy and learn practical ways to better understand your emotions, build self-awareness, and improve your emotional well-being in a safe and supportive environment.\n\n✨ Why join?\n? Explore your emotions\n? Build self-awareness\n? Develop healthier coping strategies\n? Complete all three sessions to receive a certificate\nNOTE: Group Chat has been registered under SEP.\n\n? Dates: 16, 23 & 30 July 2026 (Thursday)\n? Time: 3.00 PM – 5.00 PM\n? Venue: Student Activity Room\n\n? Scan the QR code on the poster or click the link below:\nhttps://forms.gle/J8VJko3bDR9S2ngPA (NOTE: FOR SEGIAN STUDENT KOTA DAMANSARA ONLY)\n? Limited seats available—register early!','2026-07-16 15:00:00','Student Activity Room',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783934713/s0qlkyptqy4lmiutzl9a.png'),(86,20,'PSCHYOLOGY SEMINAR AND WEBINAR','PSYCHOLOGY SEMINAR AND WEBINAR\nUnderstanding Counselling & Clinical Psychology in Today’s World\n\nEver wondered what truly differentiates a counsellor from a clinical psychologist?\nOr how complex psychological concepts can actually be applied in real life? ?\n\nJoin us for an insightful and engaging session where we will:\n\n? Break down the roles of Counselling vs Clinical Psychology\n? Simplify complex clinical concepts into practical “Mental Health Literacy”\n\n? Date: 18th March 2026 (Wednesday)\n? Time: 2:00 PM – 4:00 PM\n? Venue: Auditorium A, SEGi University\n? Open to all SEGi students!\n\n? Register now: https://forms.gle/NCW2qY9gmZbvvtiq5\n\nDon’t miss this opportunity to gain real-world insights into counselling and clinical psychology. ✨\n\n✅ SAVE THE DATE\n✅ INVITE YOUR FRIENDS\n✅ SECURE YOUR SEAT\n\nSee you there! ?','2026-03-18 14:00:00','Auditorium A',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783936467/m84lu3lkctz4mky9f7al.png'),(87,20,'MENTAL HEALTH IN THE  DIGITAL ERA','? INVITATION TO FORUM\n\nDear Students,\n\nYou are warmly invited to attend the forum:\n\n? MENTAL HEALTH IN THE DIGITAL ERA:\n_Cyberbullying, Social Media Addiction & Substance Use Among Young Adults_\n\n? Date: 6th March 2026 (Friday)\n⏰ Time: 2.30 PM – 5.30 PM\n? Venue: Auditorium A\n✨ Opening Ceremony by:\nDatin Seri Azlin Hj. Hezri\nPenaung, PCKKM\nTimbalan Pengerusi, KASIH Malaysia\n\nThis forum will explore the psychological impact of cyberbullying, excessive social media use, and substance use among young adults — issues that are highly relevant to us today.\n\n? SEP points will be awarded.\n\n? Please register using the QR code on the poster or via the registration link provided.\n\nYour presence and participation are highly encouraged. Let’s learn, reflect, and grow together.\n\nThank you and see you there!','2026-03-06 14:30:00','Auditorium A',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783936986/qvazrmclprtpl3hdfcd4.png'),(88,17,'MCS WEEK','MCS Week datang balik, geng! ?\nJom kita berkumpul, makan, shopping dan enjoy vibes bersama. Jangan ketinggalan!\n\nMCS week is making a comeback!\nVendors, vibes, and plenty of surprises.\nKeep your eyes peeled ?','2026-06-09 10:00:00','MPH & Cafeteria',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783941996/cmigtt8sgszhmhzaj4ch.png'),(89,17,'MALAY CRAFT DAY','Malay Craft Day is BACK‼️??\n\nRegister now to unlock a traditional workshop experience with MCS! ? Bringing back our childhood nostalgia with FREE traditional games to immerse in at the venue and creative workshops (12 PM to 1.30 PM) such as:\n\n? Batik Painting\n? Batu Seremban Embroidery\n?Songket Bookmark\n\nCome join the fun at:\n?: SEGi University, Dome\n⏰️: 11 A.M to 3 P.M\n?: 23rd to 25th June','2026-06-23 11:00:00','Dome',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783942199/sjnvpc2bu8mcwyrmgv2i.png'),(90,36,'命运让我们相遇','《缘·聚》新春晚宴司仪招募公告\n\n2026 年世纪大学华文学会新春晚宴《缘·聚》现正式展开司仪招募。\n本次晚宴以「缘分相遇，团圆相聚」为主题，诚挚邀请具备主持热忱与舞台表现力的同学加入，共同为来宾呈献一场温馨而难忘的新春盛宴。\n\n✨ 招募条件：\n▪ 男女不限，年龄不限\n▪ 口齿清晰，具良好语言表达能力\n▪ 能以中文及英文进行主持\n▪ 自信大方，具备舞台魅力\n▪ 反应灵敏，具即兴应变能力\n▪ 能带动现场气氛，并掌控整体流程节奏\n▪ 愿意配合相关排练与筹备安排\n\n? 加入我们，你将会\n成功入选者将担任新春晚宴司仪，于舞台上以声音串联团圆与祝福的每一个瞬间；并与策划团队密切合作，共同打造一场具温度与意义的新春晚宴，同时累积宝贵的舞台主持与活动执行经验。\n\n? 活动详情：\n? 日期：2026 年 2 月 28 日（星期六）\n⏰ 时间：7.00pm – 10.00pm\n? 地点：MPH, SEGi University Kota Damansara\n\n? 报名方式：\n有兴趣的同学请扫描二维码填写报名表单\n? 报名截止日期：16/1/2026\nhttps://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeXYRIjVl6-fQ_ybc2GeO-YR4cMW1AjN0w4YmVcYpjfb8tovQ/viewform\n\n? 如有任何疑问，欢迎联络：\n罗慧琪：018-660 9588\n颜有丙：011-1674 8233\n张嘉惠：017-757 5328','2026-02-28 19:00:00','MPH, SEGi University Kota',2,'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhzxwmkfk/image/upload/v1783942856/kodiorojlae1ssgqwbvb.png');
